<p>In a sample of UCU students, you want to investigate whether the personality trait “extraversion” predicts the number of off-campus friends a student has. However, you are concerned that your results might be influenced by the fact that Dutch students might have more off-campus friends than international students, on average. How could you best address this problem?</p>
</p>]]></text>
